<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_148" id="74r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l11"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Dyetrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hofer Rıtter </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l12">Lieber her Dyetrich / Vns hat hans Mawrer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener / als vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l13">den nehſt cʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> hercʒog <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> geſant heten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l14">als von des vnvvillens wegen den der Edell <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der von <expan>Abe<ex>n</ex>ſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l15">cʒu vns maint <expan>cʒuhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / wol geſagt wie Jr Jm darynne gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l16">dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rcʒog</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> ewr günſtige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> be </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l17">vveiſet habt / des vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ dancken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l18">vnd ſenden <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber cʒu <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rcʒog</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l19"><expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> hanſen Mawrer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener / dauon cʒureden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l21">vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan></del> diener 
<add><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l20">aber ewr </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> g ewr gün </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l22">günſtige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gen dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>hercʒ<ex>og</ex></expan> heinrıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l23"><expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweiſen wöllet Als etc das wöllen etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l24">Harprehten Harſkircher <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_148" id="74r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Dyetrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Hofer, ritter </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Dyetrich, uns hat Hans Mawrer, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        diener, als wir den nehst czu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigen
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog
                            <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> gesant heten als von des unwillens
                        wegen, den der edell <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der von
                                <expan>Abe<ex>n</ex>sp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> czu uns maint <expan>czu
                                hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> wol gesagt, wie ir im darynne gen dem
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> ewr günstige
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweiset habt, des wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz
                        dancken. Und senden <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber czu
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Hansen
                        Mawrer, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, davon czu reden. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener <add>aber ewr</add> günstige
                                <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gen dem
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>hercz<ex>og</ex></expan> Heinrich <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        beweisen wöllet, als etc. Das wöllen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Harprehten Harskircher <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
